import { useEffect, useState } from "react" import { fetchAllStudentWorksheets } from './services/worksheetServices' export const StudentHome = ({ user }) => { const [studentWorksheets, setStudentWorksheets] = useState([]) const handleStudentWorksheetFetch = () => { fetchAllStudentWorksheets().then((data) => { const filteredData = data.filter((dataset) => dataset.studentId === user.studentId * 1) setStudentWorksheets(filteredData) }) } useEffect(() => { handleStudentWorksheetFetch() }, [user.studentId]) return (

Welcome {user.firstName}

{user?.aboutMe}

{studentWorksheets.length} worksheets to complete
Click on the icon to select a worksheet.
No spam
Officia excepteur ullamco ut sint duis proident non adipisicing. Voluptate incididunt anim.
) }
